FileStateStore.Load reads .drift/state.xml from disk, unmarshals XML into Specs, Markers, and Edges, and returns the State. State.xml version=4 is the provenance-closure format: baseline only, no &lt;edgeResolutions&gt;. Pre-v4 files are refused with ErrStateVersionUnsupported, directing the user to delete .drift/ and re-init. If the file does not exist, it returns ErrStateNotFound.